  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK802">
<l>naṭpiṟ kuṟuppuk keḻutakaimai maṟṟataṟ</l>
<l>kuppātal cāṉṟōr kaṭaṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The constituents of friendship are (things done through) the right of intimacy to be pleased with such a right is the duty of the wise.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
